com.interpss.core.net.nb

Interface NBSwitch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NBSwitchImpl

    public interface NBSwitch
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'NB Switch'. Node-breaker model switcher class

    The following features are supported:

    • Substation
    • From NB Node
    • To NB Node
    • Switch Type
    • Normal Status
    • Xpu
    • Name Rating
    See Also:
    NBModelPackage.getNBSwitch()
